        "message": "LU-8139 osc: correctly parse osc.*.max_pages_per_rpc\n\nosc.*.max_pages_per_rpc is special, it can take number\nof pages or it also accepts number of bytes if the number is\nmore than 1M, this is to have uniform IO sizes on platforms\nthat have varying page sizes.\nCall lprocfs_str_with_units_to_s64 ith default unit of '%'\nwhich means \"no units\", but allow the user to overrride by\nsupplying their own units.\n\nChange-Id: I1ff4cc1848a14e42dcd05967e3e9341720c7042b\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\n"
      },
